WEBVTT

02:17.125 --> 02:19.416
What? I was sleeping.

03:35.166 --> 03:36.708
Let's break his knees.

12:21.875 --> 12:24.500
The prince didn't pay you?

14:08.250 --> 14:09.291
Eat.

14:12.625 --> 14:13.750
What does that mean?

14:13.833 --> 14:16.125
I don't make food for you to waste it.

14:16.208 --> 14:17.500
Nonna, he said no.

14:17.583 --> 14:20.791
The skinny little thing needs to eat.

14:20.875 --> 14:23.708
He's not a prince, he's a stick figure.

14:23.791 --> 14:25.041
Nonna, enough!

14:25.125 --> 14:27.375
What? He can't understand me.

14:35.833 --> 14:37.125
Eat.

16:11.041 --> 16:14.833
Isabella will show you.

22:07.541 --> 22:11.083
You and I will stay here
and take care of the salon.

22:11.166 --> 22:14.166
Let the girls go and have fun.

1:22:02.791 --> 1:22:05.958
There was nothing
we could do. It all went up so fast.

1:24:09.375 --> 1:24:12.916
Leave the poor girl.
She's been through a lot.

1:24:31.916 --> 1:24:33.875
We always have Chianti.

1:27:14.500 --> 1:27:15.375
Isabella.

1:27:16.000 --> 1:27:17.833
You are the stars.

1:27:17.916 --> 1:27:22.083
The light of my life
I've always looked for.

1:27:22.583 --> 1:27:27.333
Together, we can change the world.
